data.meta_description:
112 likes, 10 comments - charitymadeit on January 21, 2024: "“Rise Above” 
•
Honored to be apart of the Pillars of Hope at @atpromiseatl .
•
It was a full circle moment to paint a mural in my first neighborhood I lived within Atlanta.  It brought back memories of when I was lucky to have $5 in my pocket to buy dinner. But, I had a whole lot of hopes and dreams of what living in my purpose could be.
•
Thank you @atlplanning & @atpromiseatl for the collaboration for something far bigger than us!
•
And, thank you @jamanichavis for being an amazing partner! Couldn’t have powered through without you.
•
•
•
#atl #atlanta #muralist #publicart #hope #dream #womenwhopaint #riseabove #englishave #englishavenueatlanta".
